{"word":"ἀγνωμοσύνη","slug":"ἀγνωμοσύνη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγνωμοσύνη</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀγνώμων'><el>ἀγνώμων</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>want of sense, folly</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>: <i>senseless pride, arrogance</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>want of feeling, unkindness, unfairness</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>misunderstandings</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}